				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Pallava" redirects here. For the Pallava script, see <a href="Grantha_alphabet" title="Grantha alphabet">Grantha alphabet</a>.</div>
