<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_History_of_South_Asia" title="Template:History of South Asia"><span title="View this template" style="">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="Template_talk_History_of_South_Asia" title="Template talk:History of South Asia"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">t</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Template_History_of_South_Asia&action=edit.php.html"><span title="Edit this template" style="">e</span></a></li>
